@node us "Starting the program"

 Usage:

 > HType <file>

 file can be the path to any kind of file.

 Press CTRL-C at any time to stop the program.

@endnode

@node ft "Filetypes"

 HType recognizes the following file types:

 Executables
 IFF
 GIF
 PCX
 DMS archives
 Icon (.info)
 Powerpacker files
 ZIP archives
 Sound Arranger files
 AmigaGuide
 Lha files
 C object files
 AmiNet readme files
 DBTools databases

@endnode
